sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User
participant App as Commit History Webview
participant Router as HistoryMessageRouter
participant Registry as RepositoryRegistry
participant UseCase as CherryPickCommitUseCase
participant Worktree as Worktree implements WorktreeOperationCapabilities
participant Runtime as HybridGitRuntime
participant Cli as CliGitRuntime

User->>App: Cherry-pick commit
App->>Router: history/cherryPick(worktreeLocator, commitHash, requestId)
Router->>Registry: resolveWorktree(worktreeLocator)
Registry-->>Router: Worktree
Router->>UseCase: execute(Worktree, commitHash, signal)
UseCase->>Worktree: cherryPick(commitHash, signal)
Worktree->>Runtime: cherryPick(executionContext, commitHash, signal)
Runtime->>Cli: cherryPick(executionContext, commitHash, signal)
alt Cherry-pick succeeds
  Cli-->>Runtime: success
  Runtime-->>Worktree: success
  Worktree-->>UseCase: success
  UseCase-->>Router: success
  Router-->>App: history/cherryPickResponse(requestId)
  Router-->>App: history/refreshRequested
else Cherry-pick conflicts
  Cli-->>Runtime: conflict error with conflicted paths
  Runtime-->>Worktree: conflict error with conflicted paths
  Worktree-->>UseCase: conflict error
  UseCase-->>Router: conflict state
  Router-->>App: history/conflictPush(conflictState)
end
